  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      a clinical study of Ginseng its potential affect on diabetes
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Comparing three groups (those with &amp; without normal blood sugar levels) to see if there is
      any clinically significant change in blood sugar levels in relationship to those taking:

        1. ginseng

        2. ginsenoside RE (a type of metabolized ginseng)

        3. placebo
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
